begin\": 336, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9893954956477928, \"rank\": 0.01009466497126962, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sami_Brady\", \"score\": 0.5394292077652137, \"rank\": 0.6155930820508904, \"text\": \"Samantha\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sami_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sami_Brady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Catantan powered through issues on her left knee and advanced to the round of 32 of the women's individual foil after a come-from-behind 15-13 victory over Brazil's Mariana Pistoia at the Grand Palais on Sunday, July 28.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8712362837928203, \"rank\": 0.14436510688837528, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"score\": 0.9973246642220684, \"rank\": 0.0026820682713822198, \"text\": \"Pistoia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Down 11-12, Catantan - the Philippines' first female fencer to qualify for the Olympics - closed it out by winning four of the next five points to set up a clash with top seed and two-time world champion Arianna Erigo of Italy.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9667378844525396, \"rank\": 0.033907010587856064, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Vanderpool-Wallace\", \"score\": 0.9999999994872724, \"rank\": 4.757691743463337e-10, \"text\": \"Arianna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Vanderpool-Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Vanderpool-Wallace\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9983401737929327, \"rank\": 0.0013494676724419058, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chances of reaching the next round looked bleak for Catantan early as she trailed 4-7 in the first period and appeared to hurt her left knee, which she injured in the Southeast Asian Games in Phnom Penh, Cambodia, last year.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999986719104, \"rank\": 1.2133293830751251e-09, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phnom_Penh\", \"score\": 0.9999997245463799, \"rank\": 2.7402177845893956e-07, \"text\": \"Phnom Penh\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped